data.description: Short Sale Approved at Purchase Price! Nestled in the heart of nature, this rustic and environmentally friendly home features beautiful brick floors, solid wood doors, vigas, wood ceilings and not one, but two kiva fireplaces. If you enjoy quiet and open spaces, you'll adore this unique property that is nestled at the base of the Sandia Mountains. The home offers access to the National Forest at the end of the road, with breathtaking views of the Jemez and Rio Grande Valley from all directions on your 3.48-acre lot. The home comes with 2 bedrooms with 4 possible plus lots of bonus rooms to make your own living spaces to fit you and your family, including the detached structure to the right of the home.
